text: Circles is the eighth studio album by pioneering jazz group Soil & "Pimp" Sessions, from Japan. It was released on August 7, 2013.http://www.jvcmusic.co.jp/soilpimp/ ==Track listing== ==Additional personnel== Tim Conley aka MAST - Guitar on Track 8 "記憶の旅 (Kioku no Tavi)" ==References== Category:2013 albums Category:Soil & "Pimp" Sessions albums
